<!DOCTYPE >
<html>
<head>
  <title>Forget Password</title>
  <meta http-equiv='Content-Type' content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' />
  <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width' />
  <style>

    <style type="text/css"> @media only screen and (max-width:590px){ .c1{
    background-color:white !important; } .c3a, .c3b{ width:100% !important; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h4>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}}</h4>
  <h4>We received a request to reset your password.</h4>
  <h4>Your token for reset password is:</h4>
  <h4>Token: <b>{{token}}</b></h4>
  <p>Paste your token on the given field and change your password.</p>
  <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
    Only a person with access to your email can reset your account password</p>
</body>